section.download-android
    h2(id='guide-android').download-android__title.title
        .download-android__title-top How #[span to install it]
        .download-android__title-bottom for android?
    .download-android__try Spoiler: #[span easy]
    .container
        .download-android__row
            .download-android__image
                picture
                    source(media="(min-width: 551px) and (orientation: landscape) and (min-height: 500px)" srcset="img/android-desc.png")
                    source(media="(min-width: 551px) and (max-width: 1024px) and (orientation: portrait)" srcset="img/android-tab.png")
                    source(media="(max-width: 550px) and (orientation: portrait)" srcset="img/android-mob.png")
                    source(media="(max-width: 920px) and (orientation: landscape) and (max-height: 450px)" srcset="img/android-mob.png")
                    img(src="img/android-desc.png" alt="Favbet")
            ul.download-android__list
                li.download-android__item 1. Open the "settings" menu
                li.download-android__item 2. Choose "security"
                li.download-android__item 3. Select "unknown sources"
                li.download-android__item 4. Press "yes" and let's go
